 passengers in an enclosed vehicle can’t use their personal weapons to attack creatures and objects outside the vehicle, though they can use the vehicle’s weapons (if any).</p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","piloting":{"usedAsPilot":false,"piloting":0},"senses":{"usedForSenses":false,"senses":""},"canBeActivated":false,"isActive":false,"abilityMods":{"parts":[]},"critical":{"parts":[]},"damage":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"yMmYcsxBtzwzMh7f","name":"SAM Launcher (Ex)","type":"weapon","img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/equipment/weapons/imds_missile_launcher.webp","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p>This heavy weapon launches a guided missile that has a range increment of 2,000 feet. The weapon can target only airborne vehicles or starships. On a successful attack, the pilot of the defending vehicle can attempt a Piloting check (DC = the attack roll’s result) to halve the damage. An airspace defender has a capacity of five missiles.</p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","quantity":1,"bulk":"2","price":18200,"quantityPerPack":1,"level":12,"attuned":false,"equipped":true,"equippable":true,"identified":true,"attributes":{"sturdy":true,"customBuilt":false,"size":"medium","dex":{"mod":""},"hp":{"value":45,"max":"45"},"hardness":{"value":"25"},"ac":{"value":"5"}},"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":2000,"units":"ft","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":80,"units":"ft","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":""},"isActive":null,"ability":"dex","actionTarget":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[{"formula":